===========================================
  עבד v6 - Multi-User Self-Evolving Agent
===========================================

מה חדש בv6:
  זיכרון נפרד לכל משתמש לפי chat_id
  זיכרון גלובלי משותף לסוכנים
  Router מהיר יותר (qwen2.5:7b)
  Evaluator מהיר יותר (qwen2.5:7b)

מבנה התיקיה:
  start_agent.bat
  agent_server.py
  Self_Evolving_Agent_v6.json
  agent_data/
    registry.json
    memory_global.json
    memory_{chat_id}.json  (נוצר אוטומטית)

API:
  /memory/{chat_id}  זיכרון אישי
  /memory/global     זיכרון משותף
  /users             רשימת כל המשתמשים
  /agents            רשימת סוכנים

הוראות:
  1. שים ngrok.exe בתיקייה
  2. לחץ פעמיים על start_agent.bat
  3. ייבא Self_Evolving_Agent_v6.json ב-n8n
===========================================


===========================================
Owner/Admin additions - free/local only
===========================================
- Personal memory stays per Telegram chat_id in agent_data/memory_{chat_id}.json.
- Global memory is disabled by default to avoid mixing users.
- Admin chat id defaults to 7799410671. To change it before starting Flask:
  set AGENT_ADMIN_CHAT_ID=YOUR_TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID
- View a user's memory as owner:
  http://127.0.0.1:5000/admin/memory/USER_CHAT_ID?admin_id=YOUR_TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID
- Download a user's memory JSON:
  http://127.0.0.1:5000/admin/export/USER_CHAT_ID?admin_id=YOUR_TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID
- Agents now keep score_avg, score_count, best_score and uses when evaluator scores them.
- The router sees agents sorted by quality and should prefer the better scored matching agent.
- Telegram flow indicators were added before chitchat, existing-agent, and new-agent paths.


===========================================
Turbo mode - local/free speed upgrade
===========================================
- Router LLM was replaced with a fast code router, saving one Ollama call on every message.
- Evaluator LLM was replaced with a quick local heuristic, saving one Ollama call when a new agent is created.
- Heavy mistral-small3.1:24b answer nodes were switched to qwen2.5:7b.
- New agent JSON creation uses gemma2:2b.
- Prompt history was shortened to the last 3 memory items.
- Ollama options now limit num_ctx and num_predict for faster replies.


===========================================
Mini App + live flow recorder
===========================================
- Mini App local URL:
  http://127.0.0.1:5000/app
- Static upload folder:
  mini_app/
- Flow events are saved per user:
  agent_data/flow_{chat_id}.json
- Workflow now records:
  decision, selected agent, reason, inner thought, top candidates, saved result.
